1. Added this section to the end of ProteinShop.cfg to use the AMBER energy. 
2. Copy libAmber_XX.so to libAmber.so, where XX is your operating system either linux
or darwin.

Section EnergyCalculator
    addCaps true
    conTol 1.49012e-08
    fcnTol 1e-12
    gradTol 6.05545e-08
    lineSearchTol 0.0001
    maxStep 1e+20
    maxIter 100000
    maxBacktrackIter 5
    maxFeval 1000
    minStep 1e-20
    stepTol 1e-9
    verboseThreadTrace true
    maxBuffer 1073741824
    autoSaveGLState true
    sliceFactor 0.707
    textureCaching true
    updateInterval 10
    interpolationMode 1
    renderingMode 1
    textureFunction 0
    voxelAlignment 1
    dsoName ../lib/libAmber.so
    enginePath ../lib
EndSection
